act</a><a href="/privacy-policy" class="dropdown-link w-dropdown-link">Privacy Policy</a></nav></div></nav><div id="w-node-_7dbd73bf-e274-c7d4-2781-fa51868e950d-868e94e9" class="right-nav"><a href="/contact" data-w-id="7dbd73bf-e274-c7d4-2781-fa51868e950e" class="button-primary-1-icon mobile-hide w-inline-block"><div>Contact us</div><div class="button-primary-icon-wrap"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6756c558622788afc19a5f32_arrow-icon.svg" alt="Arrow Icon" class="button-icon"/><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6756c558622788afc19a5f32_arrow-icon.svg" alt="Arrow Icon" class="button-hover-icon"/></div></a><div class="menu-button w-nav-button"><div class="w-icon-nav-menu"></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class="pricing-hero-section section-spacing-bottom"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div data-w-id="dc3beaff-90aa-6535-a961-eea4e1f14f72" style="opacity:0" class="w-layout-grid grid-pricing-hero"><div class="pricing-hero-title-wrap"><h1 class="pricing-hero-title">Our pricing plans</h1><p class="pricing-hero-description">Our pricing plans are designed to offer flexibility and value, ensuring you receive the highest quality cleaning services at a fair price.</p></div><div class="pricing-hero-image-wrap"><img sizes="(max-width: 479px) 94vw, (max-width: 991px) 96vw, (max-width: 1279px) 95vw, (max-width: 1919px) 96vw, 1520px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/675915d57943f717b2dbcc30_contact-image-02-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/675915d57943f717b2dbcc30_contact-image-02.avif 990w" alt="Contact Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/675915d57943f717b2dbcc30_contact-image-02.avif" loading="eager" class="pricing-hero-image"/></div></div></div></section><section class="bg-pricing-section section-spacing"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid grid-pricing"><div data-w-id="66540b38-a6cc-beb8-8557-df732b050a06" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-white"><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price">$19</h2><div>/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title">Basic cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description">Ideal for regular maintenance of your home or office.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Dusting</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Vacuuming</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Sweeping and mopping</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Surface cleaning</div></div></div></div><a href="/contact" class="button-primary-1 w-button">Get started</a></div><div data-w-id="66540b38-a6cc-beb8-8557-df732b050a26" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-white"><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price">$59</h2><div>/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title">Standard cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description">Includes all services in the Basic package plus additional services.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Everything in basic cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Bathroom scrubbing</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Kitchen appliance cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Baseboard and trim cleaning</div></div></div></div><a href="/contact" class="button-primary-2 w-button">Get started</a></div><div data-w-id="66540b38-a6cc-beb8-8557-df732b050a46" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-white"><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price">$119</h2><div>/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title">Deep cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description">Perfect for seasonal cleaning or move-ins/outs.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Everything in standard cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Carpet cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Window washing</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>High dusting (e.g., ceiling fans)</div></div></div></div><a href="/contact" class="button-primary-1 w-button">Get started</a></div></div></div></section><section data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e24" style="opacity:0" class="faq-section section-spacing"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-medium w-container"><div class="section-title text-center"><h2 class="no-margin">Frequently asked questions</h2></div><div class="faq-wrap last"><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e2b" class="accordion-heading"><h3 class="accordion-title">What services do you offer?</h3><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We offer a comprehensive range of cleaning services, including residential cleaning, commercial janitorial services, carpet cleaning, window washing, and deep cleaning. Our services are tailored to meet the unique needs of each client.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e38" class="accordion-heading"><h4 class="accordion-title">How do I book a cleaning service?</h4><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">Booking a service is easy! You can schedule an appointment online through our website, give us a call, or send us an email. Our customer service team is ready to assist you with your booking.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e45" class="accordion-heading"><h5 class="accordion-title">What is your cancellation policy?</h5><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We understand that plans can change. If you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment, please contact us at least 24 hours in advance. Cancellations made less than 24 hours before the scheduled service may incur a fee.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e52" class="accordion-heading"><h6 class="accordion-title">Can I request the same cleaning team for each visit?</h6><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We strive to provide consistency for our clients. If you prefer the same cleaning team for each visit, please let us know, and we will do our best to accommodate your request.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item last"><div data-w-id="0765b6a7-73e3-3131-51e5-72b333023e5f" class="accordion-heading"><h6 class="accordion-title">Do I need to be home during the cleaning?</h6><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">It’s up to you! You can choose to be present during the cleaning, or you can provide us with access to your home or office. Our trusted staff will ensure your property is secure and well-cared for.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="cta-section section-spacing-top"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid grid-cta"><div id="w-node-_29fb8fe7-6b45-6903-c868-ad3a1019a3ea-5c7512b9" class="cta-image-wrap"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757dc96d4f3d3986f22981e_decoration.png" alt="Decoration" class="cta-image"/></div><div data-w-id="29fb8fe7-6b45-6903-c868-ad3a1019a3ec" style="opacity:0" class="cta-content"><h2 class="cta-title">Download now and start cleaning smarter</h2><div class="cta-list"><h3 class="cta-list-title">Key Features:</h3><div class="cta-list-wrap"><div class="cta-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6710f912b08f2b5f7beec811/67137e77825a5682ba4c1c70_check-icon-01.svg" alt="" class="cta-list-icon"/><div>Easy Booking: Schedule cleaning services in just a few taps.</div></div><div class="cta-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6710f912b08f2b5f7beec811/67137e77825a5682ba4c1c70_check-icon-01.svg" alt="" class="cta-list-icon"/><div>Real-Time Tracking: See when your cleaner is on the way.</div></div><div class="cta-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6710f912b08f2b5f7beec811/67137e77825a5682ba4c1c70_check-icon-01.svg" alt="" class="cta-list-icon"/><div>Flexible Payments: Securely pay through the app with multiple payment options.</div></div></div></div><div class="app-icon-wrap"><a href="https://www.webestica.com/" target="_blank" class="app-icon-link w-inline-block"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757dc96d4f3d3986f22981d_app-icon-01.svg" alt="App Icon" class="app-icon"/></a><a href="https://www.webestica.com/" target="_blank" class="app-icon-link w-inline-block"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757dc96d4f3d3986f22981c_app-icon-02.svg" alt="App Icon" class="app-icon"/></a></div></div></div></div></section><footer class="footer"><div class="container w-container"><div d